survey_response.review_text:
We reached out to Dr. Tina for our newborn baby who wasn’t being discharged from the NICU because they kept telling us that the Glucose levels were low. I sent her all the reports through WhatsApp and she literally understood the urgency and worries I had and assisted her with her opinion right away on call. I insisted on knowing the mode of payment for her consultation but she politely refused and said it’s not a big deal and we can pay when when we visit her. We visited her clinic in a day and she very patiently attended to our worries and worked out on the care plan for the baby that we were most comfortable with, without scaring the heck out of us. Which is extremely rare in my personal experience with doctors in Delhi.  We consulted Dr. Tina for our firstborn for newborn care, and when we decided to have our second, we had no doubts we would continue our journey with her despite moving further away from Dwarka. 
Thank you Doctor!!!! We are blessed to have found you for our babies.

I am taking my two year old son to Dr. Tina since his birth. I have always found her very friendly to parents, shares her knowledge well, and handles every child with patience and a streak to her smile. Her diagnosis and treatment are very useful, which I feel are very comfortable and I go back to her everytime. And not just treatment of our son, she actually helped us in right  way through her counselling during the first days of parenting. The best feedback I would share is my son feels happy to visit her!! 

Thanks Dr. Tina and All the best for your future.

We have been consulting Dr. Tina for our daughter for over 6 yrs now. And we can confidently say that she is one of the best paediatrician. She has got all the good qualities that young parents would want in their child's doctor. She is - patient, she will give you time, she will explain the problem, she will never cause panic and the best and the most important thing... she will provide you the right treatment and nutrition advice. And she is always a phone call away. We are blessed to have found her.

I am writing this feedback with 100% guaranteed satisfaction with the treatment of my 4year old boy child. Since the delivery till writing this feedback Dr. Tina Goel is best paediatrician I've encountered till date. She a good listener  and explains what's the problem and how we are going to deal with it. 

Fees is also not so much like most of the doctors charges in dwarka sub city. 

On a very personal note she's the only doctor I've encountered who answers her phone at 2am when there's an emergency for my child. 

Doctor friendly: 10/10
Prescription works: 10/10
Fees: 10/10
Recommended: 100/100

It seems like giving way of earning to another doc because she was ready with vsiying card. May I am wrong  and pray that she understood our concern and that Psychiatrist will help us.
